# DurationInput

`DurationInput` handles inputting time spans in a human-readable format,
providing a plain `number` to the consumer representing the entered duration as a
number of seconds.

{% showcase %}
```
<Stack spacing="space-md">
  <DurationInput value={duration.value} onValueChange={duration.onChange} />
  <Text>Duration value is {duration.value} seconds</Text>
</Stack>
```
{% /showcase %}
